rows.label: qev041604_MSG0001
rows.name:
Oh, it is friend! Welcome back!
Kuta glad to see friend is safe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041604_MSG0002
rows.name:
Er, but did friend find the huge thief thing?
What about cargo?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041604_MSG0003
rows.name: Oh-ho-hoooo! Yes! That is freight of Kuta![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041604_MSG0004
rows.name:
Long-lost sacred treasure of Nopon everywhere is
finally restored![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041604_MSG0005
rows.name:
...Okay, that last part was exaggeration.
It is really only run-of-the-mill cargo.
But Kuta just so EXCITED![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041604_MSG0006
rows.name: What happened to huge thief thing? Did friend fight it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041604_MSG0007
rows.name:
Whaaaat?! Friend defeated it?! Wow!
Kuta had no idea friend was actually decent fighter.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041604_MSG0008
rows.name:
It seems Kuta was lucky to ask friend for help.
That kind of luck crucial skill for merchants.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041604_MSG0009
rows.name:
And now reputation of Kuta for never missing delivery
lives on. Kuta can return to work with head held high.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041604_MSG0010
rows.name:
Friend is real lifesaver. Or job-saver, at least.
Kuta is sure great things await friend down the line.
But Kuta have no idea what, so best to keep it vague.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041604_MSG0011
rows.name:
Now, Kuta off! Big or small, courier Kuta gets
cargo where it is going.[ST:wait ]
